data.description:
3 bedroom, 2 and-a-half bathroom townhome with a garage in the Pine Ridge Community, available today!. Nestled in the north end of Riverview you're conveniently located to the highway, crosstown expressway, restaurants, theaters, shops, and more! As far as the townhome is concerned you have ceramic tile throughout the main floor with dark granite countertops in the kitchen and full bathrooms. Cozy carpeting compliments the top floor where you'll find your 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms along with an upstairs laundry area. With an open-concept layout and privacy upstairs, this townhome is great for entertaining. Schedule your showing today before this one is gone! 

Discounts given for multi-year leases

To prequalify or apply, please complete the following steps. 

Step 1. Download the RentRedi app 
Step 2. Tap the "Apply" button

Step 4. Select whether you're prequalifying or applying 
Step 5. Enter in your unit code: NFC-591

Step 7. Click "Send" to submit to the landlord

This property is using RentRedi for rent payments. With RentRedi, you can easily submit rent payments, boost your credit by reporting rent payments, sign up for affordable renters insurance, and more from the app!
